================================================================================

Collected texts are not relicensed by this repository. Each item generated by
scripts/scraper.py preserves source_url, license_note, and risk_note. Before
redistributing generated corpus files, review the source license and applicable
copyright law.

For ancient/public-domain texts, prefer open sources such as Wikisource. For
modern edited, annotated, or selected editions, do not import unless the license
or permission is explicit.
